<p>One fumed: 'Men, the correct answer to “how do you feel about feminism” is “I’m completely supportive”. It’s not difficult or controversial. #TheBachelorAU.'</p>

<p>Another echoed: Sorry, but why is feminism a hard question? I may be wrong, but to me I think it says a lot about him that he thinks feminism and being on #thebachelorau can’t be conducive?.'</p>

