<p>Meanwhile, Locky was also asked by Izzy's mother what his views on monogamy were. </p>

<p>Having finally found his stride, Locky responded: 'Marriage to me is very important, as long as we're in love with each other and the feelings are there, that's all I need.'</p>

<p>The adventure junkie also added that he wanted children, much to the delight of Izzy's family.   </p>

